{"tid":425164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國漁船與港油輪相撞。中國漁船日本海沉沒","createTime":"2017-10-05T12:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T13:53:12.000Z","uid":20058,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6cec02a3a5433bbfb7f3519fd0a9c8441500b1c2","tid":425164,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T12:59:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/742068612651876/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F742068612651876%2F&d=cuQ%2FH0aRDWqbLdUaIQ1IOjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=87bc6f31\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/742068612651876/</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本傳媒報道，一艘中國漁船與香港運油輪在日本島根縣對開相撞，漁船上 12 名船員失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n事發在周四早上，在本州島根縣隱岐群島北方約 400 公里的公海，一艘中國漁船與一艘香港註冊的運油輪相撞，之後漁船翻沉。<br />\n<br />\n日本海上保安廳三艘巡邏船，已開往現場協助搜救。<br />\n<br />\n＃有線新聞　＃日本　＃日本海　＃公海　＃漁船　＃運油輪"},{"pid":"8cbefa7fe3c8b155e34509f2f0095af5955ee7f2","tid":425164,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T13:00:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79cff1bb3f58bba3b398b7ec7df638ac59933ef4","tid":425164,"uid":5490,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T13:04:31.000Z","msg":"反了反了，今次真係反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57ee4ffa370ff92d4539ddce7ab3aef47ead58e","tid":425164,"uid":4493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T13:05:13.000Z","msg":"勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ddd33ae1fc722f87b81b4b3ff9875d8f1aa81b","tid":425164,"uid":11377